Method Detail

updateBus

Complex updateBus()
                  throws InterpssException
Update the bus state using the child Network object. Return the power mismatch between the swing bus of the child Network and this bus. The mismatch is used to determine the convergence of the multi-net loadflow calculation.

Throws:
InterpssException

updateBus

Complex updateBus(Complex pq)
Update the bus state using the swingPQ, It is called by the updateBus(int) method. In case of Grid computing, swingPQ might be from a remote node. Return the power mismatch of the bus.

Parameters:
pq - bus p and q
